Description: Shiny application estimating the operating characteristics of the Student's t-test, Welch test, and Wilcoxon test in one-sample or two-sample cases, in settings defined by the user (conditional distribution, sample size per group, location parameter per group, nuisance parameter per group), using Monte Carlo simulations.
